effect.@en:
Select one of these regions: northerner, midlander or southerner. You gain one of the following Traits by region:
- As a northerner: you always succeed at Skill Tests to Resist the effects of physical Peril. In addition, you never suffer from Frostbite;
- As a midlander: you always succeed at Skill Tests to Resist the effects of physical Peril. In addition, you never suffer from Starvation;
- As a southerner: you always succeed at Skill Tests to Resist the effects of physical Peril. In addition, you never suffer from Heatstroke.
